<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ei Hukdampa chawihatna'n la chu sa'i tiu,
 Pa lungsiet I het na'nga A thihzie chu;
 A lainatna namtin kieng ah gen hitiu,
 I sik gen ding a kumsawt a A hin zie.

[V2]
 Thusim mak chuh genviel hitiu,
 Kross chunga A thihzie chu;
 Chawihatna, lopina a bawnin chang hen,
 Gitloh a I pawt theihna'n A thuok zota'i.

[V3]
 2. Lungmuonna, kipahna thu A hun puok chu,
 Eihaw di'n A nutsieh ziekin pakcha'i tiu;
 A thu awite kawm achun A nai zing hi,
 Ginumte di'n A hehpih latsak ina.

[V4]
 3. Thagau kumsawt nawpna di'n van In nuom chu,
 Eihaw dinga A siem ziekin pakcha'i tiu;
 A hehpihna lopi, gen theihloh mu'i hitiu,
 A gam a mithiengte tawh I kikhawp tieng.</lyrics>
<title>LET US SING AGAIN</title>
</song>